FT  04 NOV 92 / Council strikes
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
COUNCIL workers will strike today and hold a rally in London to protest
against service cuts and job losses in the capital. Services may be
disrupted in boroughs including Ealing, Hillingdon, Islington, Newham,
Camden and Greenwich.
